author: julianfoad
msg: Use '#ifdef' consistently rather than '#if' to test preprocessor symbols that
should be either defined or not defined. This avoids some compiler warnings.

author: julianfoad
msg: Reformat an "if" condition with extra parentheses (mainly because gcc
issued a warning) and to use our convention of putting the operator at
the start of the continuation line.

author: julianfoad
msg: Add a description to a "defgroup" directive.
(svn_stringbuf_create_ensure): Quote a literal backslash in the doc string.

author: rhuijben
msg: Deprecate svn_wc_locked() and svn_wc_adm_locked() for a new svn_wc_locked2()
that takes a wc_ctx argument and provides all information.
This allows reusing database handles in svn status and allows
removing a few more access batons later.
